  "description": "Figure-eight with high entrainment (0.6) and medium tangle (0.5) — voices phase-lock into mirror-image pairs thanks to the symmetric routing matrix. The result is a dense but phase-coherent sound: two groups of three voices, each group moving in mirror phase. Good for movement without chaos.",
